E2T4BAU.original: ~z~There's a big Celebinator shaped mess somewhere, T. He ain't gonna be blogging no more.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~他应该在哪里摔成一摊了，T。肯定是发不了博客了。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I'd hold on tight if I was you.
~z~I had to steal a ticket, and then you fuckin' blanked me.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我偷了张票，但是你他妈鸟都不鸟我。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~The Derriere launch? Maisonette's fifth birthday? You left me off the list, it was a deliberate snub.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~记得Derriere的开业典礼吗？还有9号豪宅的五周年庆？你们没邀请我，存心冷落我是吧！

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~You really don't have to show me anything. I've blogged every inch of this town.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~真没这个必要。我博客上的足迹遍布自由城。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~The stars, the designers, the club owners
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~无论是大明星、设计师，还是夜店老板，

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Get away from me. Get away from me.
~z~Where'd you go, L? I thought we were taking our friend on a guided tour of the city?
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你去哪儿了，L？不是说好要带朋友城市观光吗？

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I should hope not. Big dumb greasy lug, isn't he?
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~但愿如此吧。这个油腻大笨逼。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Get in, Lou. Don't worry, I didn't forget about the vertigo, I got you a chute.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~上来吧，Lou。别担心，知道你恐高，给你拿了降落伞。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I never want to blog ever again. I fucking hate the internet!
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我这辈子都不写博客了。互联网你他妈毁了多少人！

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~You nearly missed the fun, L. Come on board, grab your chute. He's so fucking paranoid, this one.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你差点就赶不上了，L。快上来，拿好降落伞。看这家伙，总是这么多疑。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Ask him what's gonna be in tomorrow's update?
~z~I've got ADD! I'm modern! That's why you need me.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我有多动症！我够潮！所以你们需要我。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Where the fucking bubbly then? You can't tell me I'm on a helicopter tour and there's no fucking champagne.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~酒他妈在哪呢？别告诉我空中旅行没有香槟助兴吧？

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Now this would make a good blog, wouldn't it?
~z~Yo. Do you got, like, a real name? Or do I got to call you the whatsit?
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~哟。你能说一下本名吗？还是说叫那什么者比较好？

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~This how we do tit for tat where I'm from.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我们这儿都是这么报复人的。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Does he now? I'd never thought of it that way.
~z~All aboard, Lou! Here's that chute you wanted, you really gotta get over that fear of flying.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~都到齐了，Lou！拿好你的降落伞，你啥时候能不恐高啊。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~You think we'd kiss your ass? You really are crazy.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你以为我们会跪舔你？疯了吧你。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Show our friend the sights, L. I'll take the controls.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~带这位朋友看看风景，L。我来开飞机。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Yusuf's gonna be pissed. That was his chopper.
~z~Why are you doing this? I'm a nice person.
~z~Leaving me off them lists, it was a declaration of war. So I fucking brought it.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你们不邀请我，就是在对我宣战。所以我应战了。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I'm sorry. Did I just hurt you?
~z~You thought you could play us, you arrogant fuck!
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~真以为自己有多牛逼，跟我们做对是吧！

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Am I dead? I'm dead, aren't I? Oh balls. Oh bollocks.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我死了没？我是不是死了？我日，我操。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Your problem's that you think you're operating in a vacuum.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你们的问题就是做生意脱离实际。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~You got quite a few. Now where's the champagne?
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~写了还挺多。所以，香槟在哪里？

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Oh, you remember alright. Last year's Maisonette Summer party?
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~肯定有印象的。记得去年9号豪宅的夏日派对吗？

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~He's an annoying little fuck, but I think we saw eye to eye by the end of it. He ain't gonna be giving us no smack talk no more.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~这逼崽子确实讨厌，但我们还是达成共识了。他不会再抹黑我们了。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I don't know what the coroner's gonna think went on, but we better lay low. Let's talk soon.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~不知道验尸官会怎么想，咱们最好先低调点。之后再联系。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Please. My fans will miss me so much.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~求你了，我的粉丝会很想我的。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~It's not been nice. Not nice at all...
~z~That's exactly what we were looking for. A man of your fine knowledge and exquisite taste,
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我们要找的就是您啊。既有文化，又有品味。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Hey, I was real busy that night.
~z~Yeah, you were busy alright. Sinking your fuckin' business is what you were doin'.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~是，你很忙。可你在忙着砸自己的饭碗。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Twenty thousand people read my blog. I'm reaching the world.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~两万个人在看我的博客。举世闻名啊。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~This is a very grown up gesture of yours. I thought it'd be just tit for tat from here on in.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你的处事很成熟啊。我还以为接下来就要报复我了。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~How many black marks I got in there already?
~z~You one deluded motherfucker, man. Having a website doesn't make you the scene.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你他妈有病吧，伙计。开个网站有啥了不起的。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I'm just a fucking blogger. I didn't mean anything.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我就写了几篇博客。真不是故意的。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Fun's over, man. Have a nice life.
~z~Yo dude, this all in your head, man. The internet ain't real
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~哟，哥，这都是你意淫的。网上的都是假的。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~We are a terribly long way up, aren't we?
~z~You can't do this to me. I'm a celebrity.
~z~So, it's time you asked what it's going to take to get me off your backs.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~那...轮到你们提问了，怎么做我才会放过你们。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Fair point, man. I guess we got to get better at scaring cats, not dropping them. See ya.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~也是，哥们。还是得学学怎么唬人，不是杀人。再见。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Ain't this been a nice little outing?
~z~I was on the scene, Luis. Fuck it. I am the scene. Me! Moi!
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我当时在现场，Luis。操了。我就是主角！我！我啊！

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~What's the point in going to all that trouble if he's just going to die?
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~存心想搞死他，就没必要这么麻烦了。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~You should lose some pounds, bro. You too fucking heavy.
~z~Who's laughing now, you stuck up fucking twat.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~现在还笑得出来吗，真把你牛逼坏了。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I won't be treated like this. I won't!
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我怎么是这个待遇。不应该啊！

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~We wanted him dead, we coulda done it in his sleep.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~想让他死，睡熟了再动手就行。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Who the big bad blogger now, huh?
~z~I see a blog about this, I am going to fucking kill you, bro. Don't think for a moment that I ain't.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你敢发这件事，我他妈就杀了你，老兄。别以为我不敢。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Luis, have you met our charming new friend, the Celebinator?
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~Luis，你见过咱们迷人的新朋友，名人终结者吗？

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~People are gonna thank us when he's gone, Lou.
~z~UrghUgghh. Oh, ma, oh ma. Ahhhh. I feel like shite
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~－噢妈。噢妈，啊。啊，恶心死了。~n~－看来你出了点小意外。当心被人拍下来发到网上。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Luis, how'd you boys get on after you left me?
~z~The blogs are just as important a part of the ecosphere as the clubs.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~在圈子里，博客评价和夜店本身一样重要。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~It's in the ice box. We'll get it out when we seen some more of the city.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~在冰柜里。先看会儿风景，待会儿再开。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~The world ain't gonna miss a blogger.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~没人会怀念一个搞博客的家伙。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~You a long way from the blogosphere, motherfucker.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你离博客圈很远了，傻逼玩意。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Look, I got a proposition for ya.
~z~I write a blueprint that you should follow.
~z~L, shit, you manage to arrest his terminal velocity?
~z~we'd be honored to work with you.
~z~Tony Prince died right in front of me. I've got to blog this right now.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~Tony Prince死在了我面前，得赶紧写篇博客。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~He let us use it because it's such a special occasion.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~今天是个难得的机会，他才借我们用的。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I don't know what you talking about, but thanks.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~不是很懂你在说什么，但还是谢了。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~What's that smell, man? That ain't cool, bro.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~什么味儿啊，哥们？感觉不妙，兄弟。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~It kind of looks like you had a little accident. Someone might post a picture of that online.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~－看来你出了点小意外。当心被人拍下来发到网上。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~What are you talking about? We'd never even met you.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你在说啥呢？我们都没见过你。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~It's a lovely helicopter you've got here, Tony.
~z~We got too many bloggers in this town already. Drop him.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~现在城里最不缺博主。丢他下去。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~This is a guise I wear in public. I'd prefer it if you'd call me the Celebinator.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~这是我抛头露面的马甲。~n~我还是希望你称呼我「名人终结者」。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Excellent. Blackmail is a language I know only too well.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~太好了。被人勒索我可太有经验了。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~He's an ass, but you gotta save him.
~z~You want to let go, be my guest.
~z~Let's show our friend a view of the city. Take us up above Happiness Island.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~带咱们的朋友观赏一下城市风光。飞到幸福岛上空去。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I make your jobs easier by telling you what to do.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我说你做，业务就会轻松易懂。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~You ain't dead, man. You getting a second chance at life. You a fucking miracle.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你没死，哥们。你得到了重新做人的机会。这他妈是奇迹。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~You confusing the shit out of me, Tony.
~z~Let's go. First on the agenda is a trip over Happiness Island. Get us some altitude!
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~开始吧。行程第一项，游览幸福岛。飞高一点！

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~You think you important? You ain't shit.
~z~I'd love to say this was mine, but I'm just borrowing it off a rich friend of mine, Mr. Yusuf Amir.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~很想说这是我的飞机，但这是问我的阔佬朋友借的，Yusuf Amir先生。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I want me ma. Where's me ma?

E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~要滑下去了，我操，我抓不住了。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Of course you want to take some of what the Celebinator's got, and bottle it, and put it on the fuckin' shelves and sell it.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你肯定想问名人终结者要点什么，装进罐子，然后放到货架上出售。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Well maybe if you'd stuck around, you would have had some fun. Come see me soon, okay.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~要是一起来的话，乐子少不了你的。晚点见好吗？

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Boring! I knew you sad old washed up cunts had forgotten how to party.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~没意思！就知道这俩下坡路上的老臭逼已经不会开派对了。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I got a feeling that guy can afford to write off the loss. Later, T.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~我怎么觉得一架直升机对他不算啥。回见，T。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~That's excellent news. We should schmooze these "citizen journalists" more often.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~真是个好消息。就该多找这种「自媒体」聊聊。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Luis, meet our new friend, the Celebinator.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~Luis，认识下咱们的新朋友，名人终结者。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Does that mean we got to liquidise him first so he fits in them bottles?
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~那不得先把他榨成汁，然后才能装罐？

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~I thought we'd start over the Statue of Happiness. Take us up.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~还是从幸福女神像开始吧。飞上去。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~You ain't so tough without your keyboard, are you?
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~离了键盘牛逼不起来了是吧？

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~it's another black mark in the Celebinator's naughty book.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~否则终结者的小本本上又得给你记一笔。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~What you mean "tit for tat"? You just started insulting us on your website. We ain't done shit to you.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你说「报复」是几个意思？你莫名其妙就在网站上喷我们，我们又没怎么你。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Not exactly what we were looking for, was it?
~z~Not now, Lou. We're trying to charm him.
~z~I'm sorry, bro. I couldn't stand being around that guy.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~对不起，兄弟。但我是真的受不了跟这人坐一起。

E2T4BAU.original: ~z~Luis, is just joking. He didn't mean anything by that.
~z~You better have shelled out for some real vintage, Tony, or
~z~You know what, I don't think you ever seen Liberty City like this.
E2T4BAU.translated: ~z~你知道吗，我看你肯定没以这个角度欣赏过自由城。
